<i>noun</i>: 필요량 [피료량], 필요 [피료], 필수 [필쑤], 요건 [요껀], 소요 [소ː요] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>필요량 [피료량]</dt><br>
<dd>requirement; amount needed</dd><br>
<dd>꼭 있어야 하는 양.</dd><br>
<dd>The amount required.</dd><br>
<dt>필요 [피료]</dt><br>
<dd>need; necessity; requirement</dd><br>
<dd>꼭 있어야 함.</dd><br>
<dd>A state of being necessary.</dd><br>
<dt>필수 [필쑤]</dt><br>
<dd>requirement; must</dd><br>
<dd>반드시 배우거나 공부하여 마쳐야 함.</dd><br>
<dd>A state of being required to learn or study something.</dd><br>
<dt>요건 [요껀]</dt><br>
<dd>1. agenda; important matter</dd><br>
<dd>급하고 중요한 일이나 의논할 것.</dd><br>
<dd>Things urgent or important, or to be discussed.</dd><br>
<dd>2. requirement; condition; prerequisite</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 일을 하는데 필요한 조건.</dd><br>
<dd>The conditions necessary for doing something.</dd><br>
<dt>소요 [소ː요]</dt><br>
<dd>requirement</dd><br>
<dd>필요하거나 요구됨.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of being necessary or required.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>